title: C.S.I Las Vegas S4 DVD4
description: The best series of criminal investigation(research) never produced. Using the most modern forensic technologies(skills), the Department of Scientific Police of Las Vegas, directed by Gil Grissom, must investigate complex crimes without resolving, centring the attention on the most unsuspicious details and tests(proofs) found in the scene of the crime. Produced by Jerry Bruckheimer (Armageddon, Pearl Harbour)
